{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "海因瓦尔德 第4话 真相的代价",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "啊啊，可恶！又中招了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么了？\\n发生什么事了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "嗯？哦，就是最近\\n卖的面包经常被偷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "本想着今天一定要抓住这个贼，\\n可又被偷走了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "我一直死死地盯着，\\n可在我移开目光的短短一瞬间\\n就被偷走了。到底是怎么回事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "嚯？那可真是奇了。\\n唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "你、你是什么人？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "店主……你卖的面包\\n一直摆在这个木箱上面吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "啊？啊、嗯……是啊。\\n怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "这周围的脚印……唔，原来如此。\\n谢谢，真有意思。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦！？海、海因瓦尔德！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "店主",
            "context": "这、这是怎么回事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我说海因瓦尔德，\\n你是不是知道偷面包的贼是谁了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "是啊，又不是什么难解的谜题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那你为什么\\n不告诉店主犯人是谁？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "很奇怪吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这个嘛……\\n既然都知道了犯人是谁，\\n就有必要抓住他吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "是啊。我原本也是这么想的，\\n直到那时……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？究竟是怎么回事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那已经是……\\n十年前的事了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我所居住的宅邸发生了杀人事件。\\n被杀的人……是我父亲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "海因瓦尔德的父亲，\\n是阿尔贝里亚的贵族吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "是啊，是贵族的家主。\\n所以许多人调查了这起案件，\\n但还是没能找到杀害父亲的犯人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "这起案件非常蹊跷。\\n然而我自己调查过后\\n却找到了案件的犯人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我竟然愚蠢地找出了凶手……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为什么要说愚蠢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "杀害我父亲的犯人\\n就是我姐姐的未婚夫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么会……为什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "动机很简单。\\n很多人都希望我父亲死掉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "即便说恭维话，\\n我父亲也算不上一个好贵族。\\n作为蛮横的领主，许多人都深受其害。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "所以姐姐的未婚夫\\n决心为大家除掉父亲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "然而我的愚蠢行径\\n让他从正义者变成了罪人。\\n之后他背负罪名，被处死了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "就在第二天，\\n姐姐在未婚夫的遗体前自杀了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎、怎么会这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我查明了真相，抓到了凶手。\\n但结果……\\n却让众人陷入不幸……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "海因瓦尔德……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "不过……\\n放任罪行并不一定能带来幸福，\\n这很难把握。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？这话……是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "偷面包的犯人也应该\\n受到相应的惩罚。那么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "很好……没有人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "不，很遗憾，有人哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "偷面包的原来是\\n这么小的孩子……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "没错。其实他一直\\n躲在摆面包的木箱里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "手法很简单，但对误以为\\n犯人来自外面的店主来说\\n却是个意外的盲点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "干、干嘛啊你们！\\n我、我才不会把面包给你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "本来就不是你的东西，还不肯交出来，\\n真是无耻的小偷啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "海因瓦尔德……\\n你打算怎么处置这孩子？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "既然知道了犯人是谁，\\n就不能放他走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "喂，孩子。\\n看面包的量，\\n应该不是你一个人吃吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "是家人或朋友……\\n应该还有人和你一样\\n不偷东西就没法填饱肚子吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "就、就算是，那又怎样！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "拿着这封介绍信，\\n去地图上的贵族宅邸吧。告诉他们，\\n“我被你们的家主雇用了”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "然后你就会得到工作。\\n用工作得来的报酬\\n赔偿你偷窃造成的损失吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "诶！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "如果不愿意，我就说你是小偷，\\n立即把你交给领主。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "知、知道了。我会按你说的去做……\\n可是这面包……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "有人在等着吃你偷来的面包吗。\\n算了，你快去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120061_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "谢、谢谢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好厉害……\\n你早就知道\\n犯人是什么样的人了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以才没有把他交给店里的人，\\n而是特意等到\\n没有其他人的时候才动手吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不仅找出了犯人，\\n还为犯人的将来考虑。\\n这解决办法真是绝了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "倒不至于让你夸成那样。\\n只是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我喜欢真相，喜欢解开谜团。\\n但我并不想有人因此遭遇不幸。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "再也不想……\\n让那种事发生了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}